=============
 plotter.py
=============

- it runs for python version < 3
- it draws distributions for the track pulls, residuals and resolution given a root file produced using the ClicPerformanceProcessor
- specify the name of your root file and tree in "list_files"
- more files name can be added to compare the performance among different cases
- binning and range of the histograms can be changed in lines 19-40
- more resolution plots may be added in "list_resolution_var" like in the example in lines 39-40

--------------------------------